structure.name: Producer Price Indexes by Industry
structure.description: Contains a range of producer price indexes in the Australian economy, comprising mining, manufacturing, construction and service industries. Unit of measure: Index/percent. Geographic coverage: Australia. Catalogue number: 6427.0
